title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Grimm/Birk/Zimmer Presser/Leber
description: Eric Nordquist is in for PA! He is joined by Voice of the Gophers, Mike Grimm. Then it's the Birk Bit with Matt Birk. A partial Mike Zimmer press conference. And Ben Leber joins in studio!
